  "time_ut": 1657436916,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd3\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Go to a permanent solution that pleases the people.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United States of America called on political parties in Sri Lanka to work quickly to achieve long-term economic and political solutions that would satisfy the Sri Lankan people.",
        "A spokesperson of the United States of America State Department said that the Parliament of Sri Lanka is requested to work for the betterment of Sri Lanka at this time and not for the betterment of one political party.",
        "The statement states that the United States of America calls on this government or the constitutionally elected new government to quickly identify and implement solutions that will achieve long-term economic stability that will satisfy the Sri Lankan people.",
        "The United States expressed dismay at the attacks on protesters and journalists and criticized the violence that erupted during Saturday's protest."
      ],
